    <entry>
      <title>我的第一篇技术笔记</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/22/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/22/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是博客上线的第一篇技术笔记，用来测试排版和功能（缓存刷新）。</p><h2 id="环境"><a href="#环境" class="headerlink" title="环境"></a>环境</h2><ul><li>Hexo 7.x</li><li>NexT 主题（Pisces 布局）</li><li>部署在 GitHub Pages</li></ul><h2 id="代码块示例"><a href="#代码块示例" class="headerlink" title="代码块示例"></a>代码块示例</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">hello</span>(<span class="params">name</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">`Hello, <span class="subst">$&#123;name&#125;</span>!`</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">hello</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;花花&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="引用与列表"><a href="#引用与列表" class="headerlink" title="引用与列表"></a>引用与列表</h2><blockquote><p>如果一个功能写得好用，就值得认真记一笔。</p></blockquote><ul><li>记下原理</li><li>记下踩坑</li><li>记下后续可以优化的点</li></ul><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>博客搭好了，接下来才是正餐：持续地写。</p>]]></content>
      
      
